metadata.content:
# Thirsty Bantha - Behind the scenes[]

Thirsty Bantha serves as the setting for the THQ Wireless-published iPhone game Star Wars: Cantina. It does not appear and is not mentioned in any other Star Wars product. The exact chronological placement of Star Wars: Cantina is unclear, but seeing as the game makes veiled references to the first Death Star and Han Solo, this article assumes it is set sometime in the Rebellion era.
metadata.title: Thirsty Bantha
